ZH: 汽车司机踩下油门，车子瞬间加速。
EN: The car driver pressed the accelerator and the car instantly sped up.

ZH: 快速踩下油门可以让自行车加速。
EN: Pressing on the accelerator quickly can make a bicycle accelerate.

ZH: 他下意识地放松了油门，车辆减速到合适的速度。
EN: He instinctively relaxed the accelerator and the vehicle decelerated to the appropriate speed.

ZH: 这辆电动汽车的油门很敏感，需要熟练掌握。
EN: The accelerator of this electric car is sensitive and requires skillful control.

ZH: 在山路上行驶时，应该轻踩油门，以免太快消耗燃料。
EN: When driving on a mountain road, it is advisable to lightly press the accelerator to avoid excessive fuel consumption.

ZH: 老师教了我如何控制油门和刹车。
EN: The teacher taught me how to control the accelerator and the brake.

ZH: 他紧握着方向盘，同时踩下油门，使车辆以最高速度前进。
EN: He gripped the steering wheel tightly while pressing down on the accelerator, making the vehicle move at its maximum speed.

ZH: 踩下油门会增加燃料的消耗。
EN: Pressing the accelerator will increase fuel consumption.

ZH: 驾驶员突然猛踩油门，使车辆急速冲出。
EN: The driver suddenly stepped on the accelerator forcefully, causing the vehicle to rush out.

ZH: 这辆赛车的油门控制得很精准。
EN: The throttle control of this racing car is very precise.

ZH: 经验丰富的司机可以准确地掌握油门的力度。
EN: Experienced drivers can accurately control the force of the accelerator.

ZH: 请轻踩油门，避免车辆猛烈加速。
EN: Please lightly press the accelerator to avoid the vehicle accelerating abruptly.

ZH: 当你感觉到马力不足时，可以适当地加大油门。
EN: When you feel the lack of horsepower, you can appropriately increase the accelerator.

ZH: 她犹豫了一会儿后，踩下了油门。
EN: After hesitating for a moment, she pressed down on the accelerator.

ZH: 汽车的油门踏板被损坏了，需要维修。
EN: The accelerator pedal of the car is damaged and needs to be repaired.

ZH: 他试图疯狂地转动油门，希望摩托车能超越前面的车辆。
EN: He tried to twist the accelerator wildly, hoping that the motorcycle could overtake the vehicles ahead.

ZH: 在紧急情况下，可以迅速踩下油门，以防止事故发生。
EN: In emergency situations, you can quickly step on the accelerator to prevent accidents.

ZH: 开车时，一定要注意慢慢松开油门，以避免猛烈减速。
EN: When driving, be sure to gradually release the accelerator to avoid sudden deceleration.

ZH: 油门的位置在汽车踏板上。
EN: The position of the accelerator is on the pedal of the car.

ZH: 他一脚踩下油门，汽车猛地冲了出去。
EN: He pressed down on the accelerator with one foot, and the car rushed out fiercely.
